ygData.msgSnippet: You can login to egroups and signoff there or send an email to: EQ_Necromancer-unsubscribe@egroups.com The moderator and users on this list can NOT unsubscribe
ygData.messageBody:
You can login to egroups and signoff there or send an email to:

EQ_Necromancer-unsubscribe@egroups.com

The moderator and users on this list can NOT unsubscribe you. You have to
unsubscribe the same way you subscribed yourself.
